rview-of-permissions" data-id=3D"overview-of-permissions">Overview of permi=
ssions</h2><a class=3D"absolute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"overview-of-permissi=
ons" data-id=3D"hab_overview-of-permissions"></a><br><p class=3D"font-norma=
l ">Rippling hosts a wide variety of data about your employees and your com=
pany. You may want to give some people the ability to see or change specifi=
c information about other employees across your company. This might be an e=
xecutive like a CEO or CFO, someone who works in a functional area like HR =
or IT, the head of a department, or an external partner like an accountant =
or insurance broker.</p><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Permissions let you m=
anage who receives what level of access and the scope of that access.</p><b=
r><p class=3D"font-normal ">Watch this video for a brief overview of permis=
sions:</p><br><iframe src=3D"cid:frame-280BE5886675F3FE8B03E9D93A7CFF32@mht=
ml.blink" title=3D"https://fast.wistia.net/embed/ - undefined" allow=3D"aut=
oplay; fullscreen" allowtransparency=3D"true" frameborder=3D"0" lazy=3D"" c=
lass=3D"wistia_embed" name=3D"wistia_embed" allowfullscreen=3D"" mozallowfu=
llscreen=3D"" webkitallowfullscreen=3D"" oallowfullscreen=3D"" msallowfulls=
creen=3D"" width=3D"620" height=3D"349"></iframe><br><a class=3D"absolute o=
pacity-0 scroll-mt-40" id=3D"about-permission-profiles" data-id=3D"hat_abou=
t-permission-profiles"></a><h2 class=3D"text-4xl font-bold" id=3D"about-per=
mission-profiles" data-id=3D"about-permission-profiles">About permission pr=
ofiles</h2><a class=3D"absolute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"about-permission-pro=
files" data-id=3D"hab_about-permission-profiles"></a><br><p class=3D"font-n=
ormal ">A <b>permission profile</b> is a collection of permissions you assi=
gn to someone to govern their access in Rippling. Permission profiles have =
three main components:</p><br><ul class=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"ite=
ms-start"><p class=3D"font-normal "><b>Assignment</b>. The group of people =
who=E2=80=99ll receive the access included in the profile. You=E2=80=99ll s=
et up <a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"h=
ttps://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D945615220635">Supergroups</a>&=
nbsp;to automatically include people based on their roles and attributes.</=
p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal "><b>Scope</b>. Th=
e set of employees for whom holders of the profile are able to take action =
or see information in Rippling. This could be a department, team, work loca=
tion, employment type, or any other group of employees who share certain at=
tributes. Again, you=E2=80=99ll manage this using Supergroups.</p></li><li =
class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal "><b>Access</b>. The level of=
 access that profile assignees receive. This includes their ability to view=
 and change information about your workforce, hire and offboard people at y=
our company, and take other actions in Rippling apps and third-party integr=
ations.</p></li></ul><br><a class=3D"absolute opacity-0 scroll-mt-40" id=3D=
"assign-permissions-based-on-role" data-id=3D"hat_assign-permissions-based-=
on-role"></a><h2 class=3D"text-4xl font-bold" id=3D"assign-permissions-base=
d-on-role" data-id=3D"assign-permissions-based-on-role">Assign permissions =
based on role</h2><a class=3D"absolute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"assign-permis=
sions-based-on-role" data-id=3D"hab_assign-permissions-based-on-role"></a><=
br><p class=3D"font-normal ">With permission profiles, you manage access to=
 Rippling by creating profiles that meet your company=E2=80=99s specific ne=
eds and assigning them based on role or attribute. For example, you could c=
reate these profiles:</p><br><ul class=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"item=
s-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">A permission profile for all of your man=
agers that gives them the ability to terminate and view sensitive informati=
on for their direct and indirect reports.</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"=
><p class=3D"font-normal ">A permission profile for your IT administrators =
that gives them access to manage devices but doesn't allow them to see sens=
itive employee data.</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-nor=
mal ">A permission profile for HR that gives them access to manage insuranc=
e and benefits, terminate any employee, and view sensitive employee informa=
tion for the entire company.</p></li></ul><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">You=
 can use <a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=
=3D"https://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D53273402848">Supergroups<=
/a>&nbsp;to assign permission profiles based on any set of employee attribu=
tes&nbsp;so that employees are automatically given the access they need bas=
ed on who they are. You can assign profiles to groups like:</p><br><ul clas=
s=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Al=
l managers</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">All =
members of the IT department at level 7 or above</p></li><li class=3D"items=
-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">All employees in the US with annual compe=
nsation greater than $100,000</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D=
"font-normal ">All full-time employees that have been at the company for mo=
re than 90 days&nbsp;</p></li></ul><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Rippling w=
ill automatically update profile assignments when people's attributes chang=
e.</p><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Watch this video for an overview of Sup=
ergroups and permissions:</p><br><iframe src=3D"cid:frame-AB03F83F7C125BA74=
6A77C11E9A7A88B@mhtml.blink" title=3D"https://fast.wistia.net/embed/ - unde=
fined" allow=3D"autoplay; fullscreen" allowtransparency=3D"true" frameborde=
r=3D"0" lazy=3D"" class=3D"wistia_embed" name=3D"wistia_embed" allowfullscr=
een=3D"" mozallowfullscreen=3D"" webkitallowfullscreen=3D"" oallowfullscree=
n=3D"" msallowfullscreen=3D"" width=3D"620" height=3D"349"></iframe><br><a =
class=3D"absolute opacity-0 scroll-mt-40" id=3D"manage-administrative-acces=
s-by-assigning-multiple-profiles" data-id=3D"hat_manage-administrative-acce=
ss-by-assigning-multiple-profiles"></a><h2 class=3D"text-4xl font-bold" id=
=3D"manage-administrative-access-by-assigning-multiple-profiles" data-id=3D=
"manage-administrative-access-by-assigning-multiple-profiles">Manage admini=
strative access by assigning multiple profiles</h2><a class=3D"absolute mt-=
20 opacity-0" id=3D"manage-administrative-access-by-assigning-multiple-prof=
iles" data-id=3D"hab_manage-administrative-access-by-assigning-multiple-pro=
files"></a><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">People can be assigned multiple pr=
ofiles. This way, you can do things like give a manager complete access to =
view and change information for their direct reports, and more restricted a=
ccess for other departments.</p><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">When an emplo=
yee has multiple profiles, they receive the <b>combination</b> of the setti=
ngs from the two profiles. For example, say someone is assigned two profile=
s.</p><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Profile 1:</p><br><ul class=3D"list-dis=
c pl-8"><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Scope is their =
direct and indirect reports</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"f=
ont-normal ">Access to manage Time &amp; Attendance</p></li><li class=3D"it=
ems-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Access to hire new employees</p></li><=
li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Can view sensitive emplo=
yee info in areas like employee profile pages and reports</p></li></ul><br>=
<p class=3D"font-normal ">Profile 2:</p><br><ul class=3D"list-disc pl-8"><l=
i class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Scope is the entire compa=
ny</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Access to ma=
nage Devices</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Ca=
n view non-sensitive employee info in areas like employee profile pages and=
 reports</p></li></ul><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">The result is that the =
employee will have this access:</p><br><ul class=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li cla=
ss=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Access to manage Time &amp; At=
tendance for their direct and indirect reports</p></li><li class=3D"items-s=
tart"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Access to manage Devices for the entire com=
pany</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Access to =
hire new employees</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-norma=
l ">Access to view sensitive employee info for their direct and indirect re=
ports and access to view non-sensitive employee info for everyone else in t=
he company in areas like employee profile pages and reports</p></li></ul><b=
r><p class=3D"font-normal ">If a person is assigned profiles with conflicti=
ng settings, they=E2=80=99ll receive the highest level of access included i=
n any of the profiles. For example, if someone is assigned one profile that=
 grants them access to view non-sensitive employee info for their departmen=
t and one profile that gives them access to view non-sensitive employee inf=
o for the entire company, then they will have access to view non-sensitive =
employee info for the entire company.</p><br><a class=3D"absolute opacity-0=
 scroll-mt-40" id=3D"next-steps" data-id=3D"hat_next-steps"></a><h2 class=
=3D"text-4xl font-bold" id=3D"next-steps" data-id=3D"next-steps">Next steps=
</h2><a class=3D"absolute mt-20 opacity-0" id=3D"next-steps" data-id=3D"hab=
_next-steps"></a><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">Before you begin managing pe=
rmissions in Rippling, we recommend doing the following:</p><br><ul class=
=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal ">Cre=
ate a permissions strategy for your company. This will help you take a thou=
ghtful approach when setting up your permission profiles. Learn more in <a =
class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"https://he=
lp.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D581036326512">how to create a permissio=
ns strategy</a>.</p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-normal =
">Understand how employee data is classified in Rippling. All of the inform=
ation in Rippling about your employees is classified so only people with th=
e proper permissions can access it. Learn more in our&nbsp;<a class=3D"font=
-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"https://help.rippling.c=
om/article?articleId=3D819409375451">overview of employee data classificati=
ons</a>.</p></li></ul><br><p class=3D"font-normal ">When you=E2=80=99re rea=
dy to start setting up permission profiles, refer to these resources:</p><b=
r><ul class=3D"list-disc pl-8"><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-n=
ormal "><a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D=
"https://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D227350197155">Overview of th=
e Permissions app</a></p></li><li class=3D"items-start"><p class=3D"font-no=
rmal "><a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:cursor-pointer" href=3D"=
https://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D360054482094">Guide to creati=
ng and assigning a permission profile</a></p></li><li class=3D"items-start"=
><p class=3D"font-normal "><a class=3D"font-normal text-blue-600 hover:curs=
or-pointer" href=3D"https://help.rippling.com/article?articleId=3D360055620=
034">Reference guide for the permissions required by app/feature</a></p></l=
i></ul><br></div></div><!----></div></div></section><!----></c-hc-article-v=
